  <name>Mo</name>
  <name xml:lang="zh_CN">Mo 编辑器</name>
  <summary>A simple Qt6 text editor</summary>
  <summary xml:lang="zh_CN">简单的 Qt6 文本编辑器</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      Mo is a modern text editor built with Qt6 Widgets. It is designed to be
      fast, lightweight, and friendly for both casual note-taking and source code
      editing on Wayland-based Linux desktops.
    </p>
    <p xml:lang="zh_CN">
      Mo 是一款基于 Qt6 Widgets 构建的现代化文本编辑器，适用于基于 Wayland 的
      Linux 桌面环境，既适合日常记事，也适合源代码编辑。
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Multi-tab interface for working with several files at once</li>
      <li>Syntax highlighting for 200+ languages via KSyntaxHighlighting</li>
      <li>Automatic encoding detection powered by libuchardet</li>
      <li>Session restore to reopen files from the last run</li>
      <li>Find and replace with case-sensitive and regex support</li>
      <li>Wayland native, no X11 dependency</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
  <developer_name>liudng</developer_name>
  <url type="homepage">https://github.com/liudng/mo-editor</url>
  <url type="bugtracker">https://github.com/liudng/mo-editor/issues</url>
  <launchable type="desktop-id">io.github.liudng.mo.desktop</launchable>
